        created in a CyberKitAutomationSession, the signal CyberKitAutomationSession::create-web-view is emitted. The user
        should connect to it and return a CyberKitWebView. The web views used for automation are special ones and need to
        be created with the new CyberKitWebView:is-controlled-by-automation construct property enabled, otherwise we will
        refuse to create the requested browsing context.

